simple concurrency primitives

           ⢰⣿⣿⣿⣆⣀    ⢠ ⡘ ⡄    
         ⠰⠞⢻⣿⣿⣿⡏⠉⠉  ⢀⣾⣠⡇⣸⠃    
         ⢀⣤⣌⣿⣿⡿⠁    ⠈⠉⣿⡟⠿     
        ⣠⣾⠿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣶⣄  ⣠⣾⣿⠃      
      ⠠⣾⣿⡃ ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠙⢿⣷⣾⡿⣻⡇       
       ⠈⠛⢿⣶⣿⣿⣿⣿⡿  ⠉⠁ ⣿⠁       
          ⠉⣿⣿⣿⣿⡇    ⢸⡏        
          ⢠⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷    ⣾⠃        
          ⢸⣿⣿⢻⣿⣿⡆  ⢰⡿         
          ⣿⣿⡏ ⣿⣿⣷  ⣼⡇         
         ⢀⣿⣿⠁ ⠸⣿⣿⡄ ⣿          
         ⢸⣿⡟   ⢿⣿⣧⢠⡏          
         ⣾⣿⠃   ⠘⣿⣿⣾⠃          
         ⠉⠉     ⠉⠉            

usage: `make help`

features:

- pthreads (inspired by goroutines) for compute-heavy tasks
- cooperative async (inspired by javascript event loop) for IO-heavy tasks
- zig/go-like defer statement for cleanup
- tiny, header-only API without any dependencies
